name: Coming Home (insert_cat)
description:
You are an Orange Candle, looking for your way home, but so is your buddy, the Purple Candle. You guys must both shine brightly to pass the level! 

Instructions:

Use the arrow or WASD keys to move the Orange Candle. The Purple Candle will move opposite to you. The goal is to trade places. Only once you are both firmly set on your corresponding plate is the level complete.
